abstract: College Football Roundup; Washington State defeats Miami, 20-14, to win Sun Bowl; other bowl games noted.
lead_paragraph: Luke Falk threw two touchdown passes for the Cougars in the first half, and Washington State’s defense bent but did not break in holding off the Hurricanes.

headline.main: Washington State Fends Off Miami’s Rally During a Snowstorm at the Sun Bowl
